Token.Abstract: Core data model class for Syndicate Article.

sourceSectionId For tracking where this article comes from: Was it from the "All" smart section? Or from a concrete section? This property allows find the earliest article in this (smart) section. From the earliest article, we could construct a paginator and load articles earlier than that.
